import React from 'react'
import Balances from './Balances'

const Main = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Balances />
      <form>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Amount of tokens to deposit" />
        <button type="submit">Deposit</button>
        <button type="submit">Withdraw</button>
      </form>
    </>
  )
}

export default Main
